  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates a novel regulatory axis where PTBP1 suppresses ferroptosis in endometrial carcinoma cells by stabilizing SLC7A11 mRNA through direct binding to its 5'UTR",
    "The ferroptosis-suppressive function of PTBP1 appears to be cell-type specific, as previous studies showed opposite effects in liver cancer cells"
  ]
